@page "/fetchproducts"
<!--
    This component was developed with assistance from GitHub Copilot (GPT-4.1).
    Copilot contributed by:
    - Suggesting the use of HttpClient and GetFromJsonAsync for API integration.
    - Auto-generating the Product class structure based on API response.
    - Recommending robust error handling for async API calls.
    - Providing efficient Razor syntax for conditional rendering and looping.
    Efficiency improvements:
    - Copilot auto-completed repetitive code blocks (e.g., error handling, property definitions).
    - Suggested concise async/await patterns for data fetching.
    - Highlighted best practices for dependency injection and component initialization.
    Optimizations:
    - Using nullable reference types for safer data handling.
    - Streamlining UI updates with conditional rendering for loading states.
    - Structuring the Product class for easy extension and maintainability.
